_sText:
This is the Deathmatch version of this map: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/20733
Click this link for a more detailed description.

This version has no weapon spawners in the beginning, no bombzone and no weapons across the map. This may not seem like much, but the normal bathroom version crashed on deathmatch servers due to the weaponspawners. I already saw some decompiles fixing this, but this is my official release of the final.

If you do not have a DM server, download this one: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/20733

No need to rate this, it has already been rated.

-SmOoth
